import React from 'react';
import { Button, Jumbotron, Container, Form, Col, Row} from 'react-bootstrap';
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css';
import './HomePage.css';





function HomePage(props){

    return(
        <Container>
            <Jumbotron id = "createSessionSection">
                <Form id = "s">
                    <Form.Row>
                        <Col>   
                            <Form.File id="custom-file" label="Choose Demo to Upload..." custom/>
                        </Col>
                        <Col>   
                            <Button variant="create" onClick= {props.onClickCreate}>Create Session</Button>
                        </Col>
                        
                    </Form.Row>
                </Form>
                
            </Jumbotron>
            <Jumbotron id = "joinSessionSection">
                <Form>
                    <Form.Row className="align-items-center">
                        <Col>
                            <Form.Control type="join" placeholder="Enter Join Code" />
                        </Col>
                        <Col>
                            <Button variant="join" onClick= {props.onClickJoin}>Join Session</Button>
                        </Col>
                    </Form.Row>
                </Form>
            </Jumbotron>
    
        
        </Container>
    )
}

export default HomePage;
